<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-12219] Lost counter writes in compact table and static columns</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-12219</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When we have both multiple nodes, a counter column, and compact storage - some writes are lost.&lt;br/&gt;
Example given in dtest below.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In Cassandra 3.0 does not work. Before 3.0 they seem to have.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
