                            <comment id="15380373" author="brian.wawok" created="Sat, 16 Jul 2016 00:38:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Failing DTest&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15395826" author="slebresne" created="Wed, 27 Jul 2016 15:17:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Indeed. The problem is that the counter mechanism in &lt;tt&gt;PartitionUpdate&lt;/tt&gt; was forgetting to deal with the static row, and the compact table is internally using a static row. The fix is pretty trivial otherwise.&lt;/p&gt;

