&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/job/pcmanus-12219-3.0-dtest&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;dtests&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;(Note that I&apos;ll include the attached dtest on commit as test coverage)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
